  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1. Game uses 7 Stripes, 7 Solids, and 1 Eight-Ball disc.\n\r\n2. The first
    coin you pocket decides your group:\r\n   - Pocket a Stripe \u2192 You play Stripes\r\n  
    - Pocket a Solid  \u2192 You play Solids\n\r\n3. Pocketing the Eight-Ball before
    clearing your group results in an instant loss.\n\r\n4. Pocket the Eight-Ball
    after clearing all your discs to win.\n\r\n5. Foul:\r\n   - Foul occurs only
    when the striker is pocketed.\r\n   - All other traditional fouls are removed
    in this version.\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
