  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "1. Game uses 6 Red balls and 6 Color balls.\n\r\n2. Scoring:\r\n   - Red
    = 1 point\r\n   - Yellow = 2 points\r\n   - Green = 3 points\r\n   - Brown =
    4 points\r\n   - Blue = 5 points\r\n   - Pink = 6 points\r\n   - Black = 7 points\n\r\n3.
    Play alternates between pocketing a Red, \nthen a Color.\n\r\n4. After all Reds
    are cleared, pocket Colors in \norder: Yellow \u2192 Green \u2192 Brown \u2192
    Blue \n\u2192 Pink \u2192 Black.\n\r\n5. Foul:\r\n   - Foul occurs only when
    the \n      striker is pocketed.\r\n   - All other traditional fouls \n     
    are removed in this version.\n\r\n6. Highest score at the end wins.\r\n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
  m_sharedMaterial: {fileID: 2180264, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
